Cell["\<\
Reading again from the figure, we find\[LongDash]this is the kind of tedious \
work that, when we turn to DC-circuits-in-general, we will want to automate\
\[LongDash]that our 12 unknown edge currents are subject (Kirchhoff's node \
rule) to these 8 constraints:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.526224021052459*^9, 3.526224183344164*^9}}],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
