Cell[TextData[{
 "but I have other fish to fry, so will not linger to do so. The latter \
result does, however, hint at a curious fact to discussion of which I do \
promise ultimately to return. ",
 StyleBox["END OF DIGRESSION",
  FontWeight->"Bold"]
}], "Text",
