Cell["\<\
we learn that (which is evident already from the graph) node #1 is \
bilaterally linked to nodes #2, 4, 5, 6 ,7, 8. 

We are now in position to define\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.525888043161785*^9, 3.525888094494841*^9}, {
  3.5258881662149067`*^9, 3.5258882041308804`*^9}, {3.52588824178168*^9, 
