 CellChangeTimes->{{3.525977485259163*^9, 3.525977499171933*^9}}],

Cell["\<\
The walker stands at each moment (not probably but) with certainty on one or \
another of the nodes, represented in the present formalism by one or another \
of the following specialized stochastic vectors:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5259775197243977`*^9, 3.5259777143928347`*^9}, 
   3.525978381809926*^9}],

