Cell["\<\
Though column vectors speak most clearly to the habituated eye, they become \
unwieldy when presented serially on the page, so I will sometimes use simple \
lists as state-descriptors\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.525983954019109*^9, 3.52598398586018*^9}, {
  3.525984052451371*^9, 3.52598410227267*^9}}],

