  CellChangeTimes->{{3.5259817385524797`*^9, 3.5259817502420464`*^9}, 
    3.525981973268601*^9}],
 ", with \"which one\" determined by the elements of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["T", "3"], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm"],
 ", which acts here like an 8-sided die. Thus"
}], "Text",
