 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["1", "st"], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm"],
 " step has taken it, which it can learn from the placement of the 1 in the \
new state vector. The following command\[LongDash]asssembled \"by hand\"\
\[LongDash]creates a different 5-step walk away from node #3 every time it is \
repeated: "
}], "Text",
