Cell[TextData[{
 "To be in position to examine the statistical properties of ",
 StyleBox["populations",
  FontVariations->{"Underline"->True}],
 " of walks it is necessary to display each individual walk as a named object\
\[LongDash]a list of lists (i.e., of successive states). That is easily \
accomplished: here is a short (5-member) list of short (10-step) walks (each \
of which departs from node #3):"
}], "Text",
