Cell["\<\
Suppose a walker begins his walk at (say) node #1. What is the probability \
that after (say) 15 steps he stands on node #n (n  = 1, 2, \[Ellipsis] 8)? \
Iteration of the transition matrix \[DoubleStruckCapitalT] supplies \
\>", "Text",
